cal-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/5c9c2cd9-64f2-4b17-bd70-a8c6bb6bfbe1.png\"/>:<br>\nHai góc kề cạnh <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/ea5ebf75-7bec-404f-b331-91d88a6700c2.png\"/> bù nhau:<br>\n<img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/785c9333-f204-4105-a2da-53018ca14b71.png\"/>.<br>\n<img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/bb12b4e4-4f0b-47e1-af3f-246f153050b6.png\"/>.<br>\n<img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/6595e2a8-177d-48f1-8ddd-63a5b210d7bf.png\"/>.<br>\n\n<b>3.</b> Tính <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/f16ac70e-871d-4160-9c67-b9b78d859ba8.png\"/>:<br>\nVì <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/41b5b15c-f6ba-49d7-aa56-a3e80a8c17fc.png\"/> và <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/c27ced89-91e4-4649-9793-714e242cd44d.png\"/> là hai góc đối nên:<br>\n<img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/02253447-aa3a-4ce5-9d4a-876facfb2eaf.png\"/>.<br>\n\nVậy các góc còn lại của hình bình hành là:<br>\n<img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/e8245d3a-0ce1-4d14-93fb-fe9d41286204.png\"/>, <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/5df70126-f498-4a04-9322-f09346114174.png\"/>, <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/d0c9233a-8037-4185-a7a7-22ecc40ce3bf.png\"/>.<br>\n\n✅ <b>Kết luận:</b> Chọn đáp án <b>C</b>.<br>",
