                "answer": "<img src=\"https://asset.moon.vn/img/chat/large/2025/10/433e2510-d872-48cf-bc51-af8d6ff74dff.jpg\" data-filename=\"\" style=\"max-width: 600px; height: auto;\"><br>\n\n🔍 <b>Phương pháp:</b><br>\nTa sử dụng các tính chất về góc của hình bình hành:<br>\n1. <b>Các góc đối bằng nhau:</b> Trong hình bình hành <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/85123d8a-b02b-4bdc-8b31-7c43c0e7ccb8.png\"/>, <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/366a4ea7-7af2-47ad-861d-0f79be319181.png\"/> và <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/08d1494e-ce36-45c2-bbfd-dcf10a4dcd4c.png\"/>.<br>\n2. <b>Các góc kề bù nhau:</b> Hai góc kề một cạnh có tổng bằng <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/2162aeda-7620-415c-9ce6-b360b01dfee9.png\"/>. Ví dụ: <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/6d2d15d4-4f92-4a45-9b85-3e6956b3c399.png\"/>.<br>\n\n✍️ <b>Lời giải chi tiết:</b><br>\nCho hình bình hành <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/0f3f4e53-1462-4b9f-8ec6-abd2231f887f.png\"/> có <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/263e0b49-d73d-4d96-b0a9-4930239adb8e.png\"/>.<br>\n\n<b>1.</b> Xét góc <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/aa4a2022-b83d-42dc-85e2-4ecfc92014de.png\"/>:<br>\nVì <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/a6d93131-bd6e-42ba-b394-d1cdd225191b.png\"/> và <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/735bc50f-9ad6-404c-bf15-7558385b576c.png\"/> là hai góc đối nên:<br>\n<img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/e84baa41-1b05-4d58-b90d-46148617d281.png\"/>.<br>\n\n<b>2.</b> Xét góc <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/957fc61d-12f2-483e-856b-01dbba826dc6.png\"/>:<br>\nHai góc kề cạnh <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/df9fd2b3-27c0-40f2-b656-60debab776df.png\"/> bù nhau:<br>\n<img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/0067f8e4-3ab8-4b6b-ab3f-735b051e82f3.png\"/>.<br>\n<img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/8a2bceff-ab4e-40b5-822a-486f7f4c3fa6.png\"/>.<br>\n<img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/61a2ed94-e534-416e-8f52-33017871abc3.png\"/>.<br>\n\n<b>3.</b> Xét góc <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/c5774422-31c6-4f11-bae8-75151694351d.png\"/>:<br>\nVì <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/55bb93b2-be68-4ab5-b4c7-d05d276385c7.png\"/> và <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/d1400283-1342-42ac-b453-0e6d4b967db7.png\"/> là hai góc đối nên:<br>\n<img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/5d0464a6-5570-4b10-ad6b-dfc2e01412c2.png\"/>.<br>\n\n<b>Kiểm tra các khẳng định:</b><br>\n<b>A.</b> <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/0f2bb712-7e76-4a56-8ad6-bed538680f7f.png\"/> → Sai (<img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/1442c9d8-1325-4fa8-83da-17d2e5d580ee.png\"/>).<br>\n<b>B.</b> <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/2cd87f4d-b10a-4421-96ff-4ad8c68eff0c.png\"/> → Sai (<img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/7ffb0765-b1f0-4e92-a351-5e8ff32a3503.png\"/>).<br>\n<b>C.</b> <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/0e23463f-892a-46ed-be4e-6c3b90a23a0a.png\"/> → Đúng ✅<br>\n<b>D.</b> <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/42fe8017-225d-4e34-a79a-5046d13cade7.png\"/> → Sai (<img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/9c5e84ab-f4eb-4357-8d3a-fdd4237f02ae.png\"/>).<br>\n\n✅ <b>Kết luận:</b> Chọn đáp án <b>C</b>.<br>",
